theorem closure_interior_closure_interior_eq
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (interior (closure (interior (A : Set X))))
      = closure (interior A) := by
  -- First inclusion: `⊆`.
  have h₁ :
      closure (interior (closure (interior A))) ⊆ closure (interior A) := by
    apply closure_mono
    exact interior_closure_interior_subset_closure_interior
  -- Second inclusion: `⊇`.
  have h₂ :
      closure (interior A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure (interior A))) := by
    -- Start with `interior A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A))`.
    have hInner :
        interior A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A)) := by
      have hIncl : interior A ⊆ closure (interior A) :=
        (subset_closure : (interior A : Set X) ⊆ closure (interior A))
      have : interior (interior A) ⊆ interior (closure (interior A)) :=
        interior_mono hIncl
      simpa [interior_interior] using this
    exact closure_mono hInner
  exact subset_antisymm h₁ h₂

theorem interior_closure_univ_implies_P3
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (h : interior (closure (A : Set X)) = (Set.univ : Set X)) :
    Topology.P3 (A : Set X) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3]
  intro x hx
  have : x ∈ (Set.univ : Set X) := by
    simp
  simpa [h] using this
